text: Federico Enrique Sztyrle (born 9 September 1964) is an Argentine equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Argentina Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:People from San Martín, Buenos Aires
